### Get all movie statuses for a user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status/user/1

### Get all user statuses for a movie
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status/movie/1

### Get a user's status for a movie (Success)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status/1/1

### Get a user's status for a movie (Failure - status not found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status/1/999

### Add a new movie status (Success)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "movieId": 1,
  "status": "WATCHED"
}

### Add a movie status (Failure - invalid status)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "movieId": 1,
  "status": "INVALID_STATUS"
}

### Update a movie status (Success)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "movieId": 1,
  "status": "WATCHING"
}

### Delete a movie status (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status/1

### Delete a movie status (Failure - status not found)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/user-movie-status/999
